      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "你有没有发现，蝴蝶的左边和右边长得一模一样？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "这种左右一样的美，数学上叫做对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "今天我们一起来看看，对称到底藏着怎样的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "mirror",
      "line_id": "mirror-1",
      "filename": "mirror-mirror-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/mirror-mirror-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "想象在图案中间竖一面镜子，左边照出来正好是右边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "mirror",
      "line_id": "mirror-2",
      "filename": "mirror-mirror-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/mirror-mirror-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.3,
      "size": 20736,
      "text": "这条镜子所在的线，就叫对称轴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "mirror",
      "line_id": "mirror-3",
      "filename": "mirror-mirror-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/mirror-mirror-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "蝴蝶、人脸、树叶，都有这样一条对称轴。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "rotation",
      "line_id": "rotation-1",
      "filename": "rotation-rotation-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/rotation-rotation-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "还有一种对称，是把图案绕着中心转一转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "rotation",
      "line_id": "rotation-2",
      "filename": "rotation-rotation-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/rotation-rotation-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "风车转四分之一圈，看起来和原来一样，这叫四重旋转对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "rotation",
      "line_id": "rotation-3",
      "filename": "rotation-rotation-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/rotation-rotation-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "海星转五分之一圈重合，雪花转六分之一圈重合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
