      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "切换不同的图案，数一数它转几次才能回到原样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "再找一找，哪些图案还能沿着对称轴翻折重合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "symmetry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/symmetry/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "对称就是变换之后还能和自己重合。"
    },
    {
